  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Placing a seal on a target in range, you further improve the condition of their armor. For the duration, while benefiting from armor that has the Advanced Reinforcement Seal, you may add your Strength Mod to the wearer's AC. Only one set of armor at a time may benefit from this jutsu.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you upcast this jutsu above B-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3. If cast at A-Rank, this jutsu instead lasts 10 minutes. If cast at S-Rank, this jutsu instead lasts 1 hour.</p>",
